creator: Picture Quiz App
descriptionHtml:
Movie Quiz app is a game for fans of movies and TV series. If it seems to you that you know all the characters from the movies, then this quiz will please you. Guess the characters of movies and TV series, get crystals for it and go through all the levels.

Special features of the quiz:
- Many characters of popular movies and TV shows
- Many levels for the quiz
- Get crystals when you guess the character
- The mode in which you need to guess the symbols from the movie
- Magnificent images of characters and characters
- Get hints if you can't guess the riddle
- Movie character quiz for the whole family
- Free movie quiz games
- The mode movie logo quiz

This application is created by fans. All rights to the characters belong to their creators. For any questions, write to trackerstatsapp@gmail.com
